trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute" /> .

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> to override the behavior of a set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> para substituir o comportamento de um conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Multiple instances of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> class can be applied to a class member, as long as each instance has a distinct <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute.Name%2A> property value; this instructs the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> to collect unknown elements under the named element into the appropriate array.
trans-unit.target: Várias instâncias do <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> classe pode ser aplicada a um membro de classe, desde que cada instância tem um distintos <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute.Name%2A> o valor da propriedade; Isso instrui o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> para coletar desconhecidos elementos sob o elemento de nome para a matriz apropriada.

trans-unit.source: It is for this reason that multiple instances of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> class can be added to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: É por essa razão que várias instâncias do <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> classe pode ser adicionada para o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: To override a set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects:
trans-unit.target: Para substituir um conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos:

trans-unit.source: Create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: Criar um <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: Create the set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects, and add each object to the collection using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Criar o conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos e adicionar cada objeto à coleção usando o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes.Add%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: Criar um <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> property to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.
trans-unit.target: Definir o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> propriedade para o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes>.

trans-unit.source: Create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.
trans-unit.target: Criar um <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.

trans-unit.source: Add the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> to the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Adicionar o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> para o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> usando o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides.Add%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Create an instance of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.
trans-unit.target: Criar uma instância do <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> usando o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides>.

trans-unit.source: Serialize or deserialize an object that contains the set of <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objects.
trans-unit.target: Serializar ou desserializar um objeto que contém o conjunto de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The following example creates a new <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> and adds it to the collection of objects accessed through the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir cria um novo <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttribute> e o adiciona à coleção de objetos acessados por meio de <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes.XmlAnyElements%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> is then added to a <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> which is used to create an <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributes> é adicionado a um <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAttributeOverrides> que é usada para criar um <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> is used to serialize or deserialize an object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> é usado para serializar ou desserializar um objeto.

trans-unit.source: To see the effect of using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> property, create an XML document named UnknownElements.xml by running the `SerializeObject` method in the `Main` method.
trans-unit.target: Para ver o efeito de usar o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> propriedade, criar um documento XML chamado UnknownElements.xml executando o `SerializeObject` método o `Main` método.

trans-unit.source: Edit the resulting document to include other (unknown) elements.
trans-unit.target: Edite o documento resultante para incluir outros elementos (desconhecidos).

trans-unit.source: Comment out the `SerializeObject` call in the `Main` method, and uncomment the call to the `DeserializeObject` method, which prints out the name and value of any unknown XML element.
trans-unit.target: Comente o `SerializeObject` chamar o `Main` método, e remova a chamada para o `DeserializeObject` método, que imprime o nome e o valor de qualquer elemento XML desconhecido.

trans-unit.source: To see the effect of using the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> property, create an XML document named UnknownElements.xml by running the `SerializeObject` method in the `Main` method.
trans-unit.target: Para ver o efeito de usar o <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlAnyElementAttributes> propriedade, criar um documento XML chamado UnknownElements.xml executando o `SerializeObject` método o `Main` método.
